      <title>FTX 债权人有望提振陷入困境的加密货币市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ftx-creditors-may-boost-struggling-bitcoin-btc-crypto-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币交易所 FTX 的债权人将在未来几个月根据法院批准的支付计划获得超过 120 亿美元的资金，这增加了部分现金可能重新投入数字资产的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ftx-creditors-may-boost-struggling-bitcoin-btc-crypto-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
